sub_title: Student International Business & Languages at Stenden University
summary: I am a third year 'International Business & Languages' student at Stenden University. I love to gain lot of experiences in different places and from different cultures. Therefore I chose to go to Indonesia and study in Bali for 5 months. I am always very motivated to achieve my goals and have excellent communication and interpersonal skills. I am currently looking for an internship position in Germany, to gain more experience in business life and to improve my German language skills.
